{"tid":82893,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[FF系列]想考樂理","createTime":"2017-01-16T10:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T03:37:24.000Z","uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6942afe8950ad1a19d8b8f3e91c3266faabe27bc","tid":82893,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"諗住每個月由一級逐級上做樂理練習<br />\n另加考前一個月做PP<br />\n6月考5級,10月就考8級<br />\n唔知有冇可能<br />\n但當係呢一年目標,嘗試下<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇巴絲都諗住今年考<br />\n開個GP交流下<br />\n雖然應該會變死group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1M1aKoKZqY26mgPB6iid0ltuAKOrZ90SUXVLd4nzxAfs/prefill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1M1aKoKZqY26mgPB6iid0ltuAKOrZ90SUXVLd4nzxAfs%2Fprefill&d=hLOWhBhG0hlTLctC6GWcNWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=a6681d14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1M1aKoKZqY26mgPB6iid0ltuAKOrZ90SUXVLd4nzxAfs/prefill</a><br />\n<br />\n或者有玩開流行想交流下都可以入<br />\n<br />\n由一級做起就知小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教下小弟"},{"pid":"f53d419ce3f2376e2cbc4830a383a91850a5d1ac","tid":82893,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1M1aKoKZqY26mgPB6iid0ltuAKOrZ90SUXVLd4nzxAfs/prefill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1M1aKoKZqY26mgPB6iid0ltuAKOrZ90SUXVLd4nzxAfs%2Fprefill&d=hLOWhBhG0hlTLctC6GWcNWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=a6681d14\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1M1aKoKZqY26mgPB6iid0ltuAKOrZ90SUXVLd4nzxAfs/prefill</a>"},{"pid":"fdb8a8170edacd0aeeb55a5d18efce3312b44138","tid":82893,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:16:35.000Z","msg