":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5級就易過借火 有讀就會丁<br />\n8級...... 你預一年啦 否則連cred都無 自己冇癮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 冇癮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n8級真係唔識考<br />\n<br />\n利申 得個pass</blockquote><br />\n同五級最大分別係咩</blockquote><br />\n5級真係合埋眼去考都識 <br />\n8級係根本要你所有野都識 仲要每樣野都係一分兩分 慘過考會考 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁仲好<br />\n咁起碼知自己係唔係識曬<br />\n冇得博大霧"},{"pid":"518db04212df91cbff7999bc6231f80880d08a43","tid":82893,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:23:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e93acedce393c9c92b4a19118ee788f3a6a6fcf0","tid":82893,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4b1ced6bc21d958faedd64fe7d1ab25d42e156f5","tid":82893,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58244a44625b6323c2170032b9f3a6945f9e1b29","tid":82893,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"8級難度高好多㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我5級慢慢學，半年都拎到99分<br />\n但8級就上堂學咗一年都未敢考住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935690071c9dc13fdc9899056ab6eda3c28b83a0","tid":82893,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8級難度高好多㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我5級慢慢學，半年都拎到99分<br />\n但8級就上堂學咗一年都未敢考住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ed6293b588eef607bf4e48368d0294930731f8","tid":82893,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>8級難度高好多㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我5級慢慢學，半年都拎到99分<br />\n但8級就上堂學咗一年都未敢考住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係太多定太深"},{"pid":"f3c7d79530a1517d31e7d275fa4b5e6f13e7f48b","tid":82893,"uid":48504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>8級難度高好多㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我5級慢慢學，半年都拎到99分<br />\n但8級就上堂學咗一年都未敢考住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係太多定太深</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多而且深 淨係figure bass都要搞一輪 我5級熟到爛晒<br />\n8級都係7x"},{"pid":"62fa98de45e643a17a207f8798a31fb4682ccd7d","tid":82893,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>8級難度高好多㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我5級慢慢學，半年都拎到99分<br />\n但8級就上堂學咗一年都未敢考住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係太多定太深</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為唔想為考試而學<br />\n所以我學得好慢，想每樣嘢真係明白咗先學下一樣<br />\n而8級樂理好多嘢平時都少接觸<br />\n於是就學得好慢"},{"pid":"d6ab32636cb70700e7258860d85aee1d28a00ab3","tid":82893,"uid":19879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"我勁蠢五級樂理都考到89分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗擔心啦"},{"pid":"3d859482eb11837e324e0c6dc6e5ef4d412896f3","tid":82893,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>8級難度高好多㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我5級慢慢學，半年都拎到99分<br />\n但8級就上堂學咗一年都未敢考住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係太多定太深</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多而且深 淨係figure bass都要搞一輪 我5級熟到爛晒<br />\n8級都係7x</blockquote><br />\nsame <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da35a775db6c12d15efcd0b6cf8bd17c4f003b4b","tid":82893,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>8級難度高好多㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我5級慢慢學，半年都拎到99分<br />\n但8級就上堂學咗一年都未敢考住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係太多定太深</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多而且深 淨係figure bass都要搞一輪 我5級熟到爛晒<br />\n8級都係7x</blockquote><br />\n唔知玩開結他<br />\n對chord 熟<br />\nfigured bass 有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5774548af2b76358fe90e68366543ac8661a6826","tid":82893,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n唔知玩開結他<br />\n對chord 熟<br />\nfigured bass 有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係學古典結他嘅<br />\n但唔覺得比起其它樂器特別有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能學鋼琴反而著數啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601af17e268f7a162332f232b4326c5a8bde8b4c","tid":82893,"uid":48504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T03:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n係太多定太深</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多而且深 淨係figure bass都要搞一輪 我5級熟到爛晒<br />\n8級都係7x</blockquote><br />\n唔知玩開結他<br />\n對chord 熟<br />\nfigured bass 有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實依家咁多件樂器有邊樣真係會出現figure bass 都冇乜 所以學完好快會唔記得 但係考試好似係一定會有 唔學唔得"}]}